high_descs: turn left and walk past the kitchen island counter on the left, then take a left and walk to the near end of the kitchen counter space on the right to face the kitchen counter space on the right
grab the dirty bowl off of the counter there
turn right and walk to the end of the room where the sink is
place the bowl inside of the sink to clean it off, then take it back out once you have cleaned the bowl
turn around and walk over to the end of the room where the three brown shelves are on your right, turn right to face them
place the bowl down on the middle brown shelf on the right side
anns.task_desc: place a clean bowl on the middle brown shelf in the corner of the room

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the sink and walk to the far counter on the right past the stove.
Pick up the dirty bowl from the left side of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the bowl inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the rack of wooden shelves on the right.
Put the clean bowl on the right side of the middle shelf on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean bowl on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the counter, then turn left and go past the kitchen island, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the bowl on the counter.
Turn around and step forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Clean the bowl inside of the sink.
Turn around and go forward to the wall, then turn right to face the shelves.
Put the bowl on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bowl on the shelf.
